headline: Humana Appoints Michelle O'Hara as Chief Human Resources Officer
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., November 12, 2024--Leading health and well-being company Humana Inc. (NYSE: HUM) announced today that it has named Michelle O'Hara as Chief Human Resources Officer, effective January 1, 2025. O’Hara will oversee the enterprise talent strategy and people programs for Humana’s more than 63,000 employees. She brings a proven track record of transforming HR capabilities and enabling companies to effectively attract, recruit, develop and retain a talented and diverse workforce. O’Har
